function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

	-- There are linked SpawnerGizmos to each Quest Switch.
	-- Enemies: 
	Hydra.ActorTriggerSpawnerUpdateLinkedToActor(idActorGizmo)
	--Grave Marker Progression
	Hydra.EventSendToActor("QST_Scos_Hills_VotivePassing_Grave", idSelf, idSelf)
	
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

--Wounded Hunter continues ellegy

if Hydra.ActorIsValid(NPC_HUNTER) then
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CONV_HUNTER_MID, idActor, NPC_HUNTER)
end

end

function Start()

--Wounded Hunter elegy is heard from a distance
local idOwner = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()

if Hydra.ActorsInSameLevelArea(idSelf, NPC_HUNTER) then
	Hydra.ActorPlayConversation(CONV_HUNTER_START, idSelf)
end

end

function Start()
	-- Attempt to Push the Quest Item
	idQuestOwner = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()
	Hydra.ItemGiveQuestItemToPlayer(idQuestOwner, "QST_Scos_VotivePassing_HandmadeTorc", "QST_Scos_Hills_VotivePassing")
end
